{"tid":1113532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加州婦以煙酒作餌　誘兩女兒未成年男友性交 睇圖幾...","createTime":"2019-04-18T03:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T07:31:28.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"109b26bf06983c81ea2e80ac744a6edbf06655c4","tid":1113532,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T03:08:44.000Z","msg":"美國加州一名中年婦人涉於前年，以煙酒引誘兩名女兒、年齡分別14及15歲的男友性交。她事後被控21項性罪行，法官周一（15日）聽取感化報告後，認為判處被告監禁6年，緩刑5年的刑期不恰當，被告下周一（22日）須再次出庭。 <br />\n<br />\n案情透露，圖萊里縣（Tulare）41歲婦人萊特爾（Jeff Lytle）於2017年秋季，多次與兩名未成年少男做愛。其中一名事主表示，他與萊特爾發生3次性行為，最後一次發生在當年10月5日。他指與萊特爾的丈夫握手時，便會想起不倫關係及感到愧咎，於是不再與萊特爾做愛。 <br />\n<br />\n檢方批評，萊特爾所犯的罪行「極殘忍無情」，並利用了兩名青少年對她的信任。萊特爾的丈夫在妻子被捕後，已申請了離婚。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190417/mobile/bkn-20190417201235885-0417_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190417%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190417201235885-0417_00972_001.html&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSNg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=84274913\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190417/mobile/bkn-20190417201235885-0417_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190417/photo/bkn-20190417201235885-0417_00972_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190417%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190417201235885-0417_00972_001_01p.jpg&h=9eed64be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e4f79a18370f5a131c6eb54a2948d6154dd3ce","tid":1113532,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T03:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089c914c845c8d2f3793c9acd33d0131fb974493","tid":1113532,"uid":225760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T03:10:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0453e664